5. Remove alsa library and folder

   $ sudo nano /etc/rc.local

     ls /usr/lib/arm-linux-gnueabihf/libasound* 1>/dev/null 2>&1 && rm /usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libasound*
     [ -d "/usr/share/alsa/" ] && rm -rf /usr/share/alsa/
     cp /etc/alsa.conf.min /dev/shm/alsa.conf

